{"tid":462435,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國製平價機械鍵盤内置監控？網民：便宜莫貪","createTime":"2017-11-08T14:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T17:40:21.000Z","uid":39464,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bee6c937a71591d6313ef64028bb333900d4b9f6","tid":462435,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:20:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1940000/1942982/keyboard01-_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1940000%2F1942982%2Fkeyboard01-_1024.jpg&h=f15c7964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n很多時大家都會對中國製造投下「不信任票」。雖然不少内地產品的價格都很便宜，但質量就難説。現在，又有另一個「不信任」的原因了。有外媒報道，表示一款中國生產的機械鍵盤「MantisTek GK2」竟然會紀錄並統計使用者打過什麽字！<br />\n<br />\n據外媒「Tech Power Up」及「Tom's Hardware」報道，有網民投訴手上中國生産的「MantisTek GK2」RGB 機械鍵盤，似乎會將輸入過的資料透過「Cloud Driver」功能發送到阿里爸爸伺服器。經過調查之後，發現使用者的輸入數據並沒有傳送到阿里爸爸伺服器，然而鍵盤就會自動統計使用者的輸入數據，代表鍵盤會紀錄使用者打過的任何字，包括密碼。<br />\n<br />\n雖然，「MantisTek GK2」RGB 機械鍵盤只會統計使用者輸入過的字，然而不少網民已經覺得頗爲恐怖。其實，這個鍵盤比起市面上的其它機械鍵盤要便宜一半有多，便宜不一定好，大家要自行衡量了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1940000/1942982/keyboard1_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1940000%2F1942982%2Fkeyboard1_600.jpg&h=733ff3f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1940000/1942982/keyboard2_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1940000%2F1942982%2Fkeyboard2_600.jpg&h=04a12104&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource：Tech Power Up、Tom's Hardware<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1942982\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1942982&d=AB%2BcY2C%2FDevFsiJ4lyasjbZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=0987f657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1942982</a>"},{"pid":"9087c8f83e670a2ccd92d712451d5791ba11492b","tid":462435,"uid":33176,"like":2,"dislike":24,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:23:32.000Z","msg":"吾系plug n play吾用<br />\n講完"},{"pid":"d55e8f629d9b6f4811589621205a6008fd9aacfa","tid":462435,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:26:42.000Z","msg":"市面同類產品多的是！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何必用中國產品！"},{"pid":"ca4102ebe583ccfd495a73e8eafe09cb49ea9afa","tid":462435,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:32:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea960056af9ac2be2bf79d1407933c2d6bd1f839","tid":462435,"uid":41245,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:38:19.000Z","msg":"行得正企得正怕咩人監控"},{"pid":"eed075341690bbe2d0e1c2cd492999c7901baa66","tid":462435,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:39:51.000Z","msg":"喺中國,話唔定連用嘅筆都有監控"},{"pid":"ff478d6604246e19e62c82856d137685ceb4a5ae","tid":462435,"uid":60695,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T15:15:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行得正企得正怕咩人監控</blockquote><br />\n唔差在分享埋你啲密碼畀呢到啲手足知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b0081818a15701dc6c7f20fc8593dc0e379141","tid":462435,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T15:43:48.000Z","msg":"唔係D大陸嘢做乜咁平呀? 蝕本價俾你? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用小米尿袋個D 都小心D. 除時有CHIP. 一插手話就自動上傳DATA"},{"pid":"ba709292ff97f72d246ee4f5b4c2b3d0811a9f0b","tid":462435,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T15:47:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4